<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>DAMALZ Technologies</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #0b1220;
        color: white;
    }

    header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 20px 60px;
        background: #0f1b33;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
    }

    header h1 {
        color: #4da3ff;
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    nav a {
        color: white;
        margin-left: 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .hero {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 100px 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, #0f1b33, #0b1220);
    }

    .hero h2 {
        font-size: 42px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero p {
        color: #aaa;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .btn {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        background: #4da3ff;
        border: none;
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .section {
        padding: 60px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .services {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .card {
        background: #121f3a;
        padding: 20px;
        width: 250px;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .card h3 {
        color: #4da3ff;
    }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        background: #0f1b33;
        color: #888;
    }

    input, textarea {
        width: 300px;
        padding: 10px;
        margin: 10px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>DAMALZ Technologies</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h2>Modern IT Infrastructure & Networking Solutions</h2>
    <p>We build secure, scalable, and automated network systems for businesses.</p>
    <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
</section>

<section id="services" class="section">
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <div class="services">

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Network Engineering</h3>
            <p>Enterprise-grade network design, routing, and firewalling.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Cloud & Virtualization</h3>
            <p>Proxmox, VMware, and cloud infrastructure solutions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Cybersecurity</h3>
            <p>Firewall setup, monitoring, and security hardening.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Automation</h3>
            <p>Ansible, Python, and infrastructure automation tools.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="section">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p style="max-width:700px;margin:auto;color:#aaa;">
        DAMALZ Technologies provides modern IT solutions including networking,
        cloud infrastructure, virtualization, and security services.
        We focus on building reliable and scalable systems for businesses and labs.
    </p>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="section">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>

    <form>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" /><br/>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" /><br/>
        <textarea rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea><br/>
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Send</button>
    </form>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 DAMALZ Technologies - All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>
